About Us

We are Agricultural Technology Company Offering wide range of services that will leave your farm healthy & Productive

How we do it

We emphasize on delivery of high tech solutions and our professionals are all equipped with up to date knowledge which will give you a competitive advantage with other farmers in the market.

Our Mission

Kasong AgroTech takes pride in providing higher quality services which will leave your farm healthy.

We do this by applying the most recent technologies and highly talented and trained staff. High return to our farmers is always in our ways of action.

item.title: Home
item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded:
[smartslider3 slider="2"]

Our Services

We are all in one package company devoting our time and energy to provide solutions to the problems facing the farmers in developing countries.

We believe that helping farmers to apply advanced technology in their day to day activities will help to stabilize their cashflow and eventually make farming as a reliable solution to fight poverty.

Greenhouse installation

We construct greenhouses ranging from manual to fully automated. Depending on your piece of land and the soil quality you can choose the dimensions and the setup you want. We also have greenhouses with soilless farming.

Agro-inputs supply

We supply high agricultural inputs that are certified worldwide. We also provide guidance on how to use these inputs and you will always get someone in touch from us to ensure better outcomes.

Market linkages

We know that farmers spend most of their time taking care of their crops in the field expecting for higher yields and eventually profit. We use our network of buyers to connect you to the market so you can sell your products at a reasonable price.

More services

We provide all services related to agriculture such as water and energy systems, farm planning and design, Fish ponds and livestock barns construction.

See complete overview of our services

item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded: Add all the tech staff you have

item.title: Farm Technology
item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded:
1. Farm mechanization(machinery.jpg)

The agriculture season starts with field preparation. we know that small holder farmers dont have the capital to buy the heavy machinery. As Kasong AgroTech, we outsource our powerful agricultural machines to work on your farm.

  1. Energy and water supply (solarpump.jpg)

If your farm is far from power supply line or you have no water source close by, you dont have to worry. We install a compliment power system including drilling wells or setting up a rainwater harvesting system, this will make your farm to produce crops year-round.

  1. Drip & Sprinklers irrigation

High water usage is among the factors lowering the farmers profit. conventional irrigation methods use more water, hence increasing your operating expenses. With our new technology you will be able to irrigate your field with the correct amount of water.

  • Greenhouse installation (greenhouse.jpg)

Our greenhouses can be customized to meet based on your demands. We install greenhouses from fully automated to manually operated. With our greenhouses you will ensure high productivity and year-round yield.

  • Fishponds & Livestock bans (include description of chicken bans, cows, and fishponds)

We are also experts in setting up and managing fishponds. We design your fishpond from the scratch, and we supply you with everything you need to get started including linking you to our experts network.

  • Farm planning and design

It is always hard to know where to locate what in your piece of land. At Kasong AgroTech, we design your farm from the scratch to integrate animals and possibility for reuse of wastes from one system to the other with easy so you can produce everything from the same piece of land.

item.title: Post-harvest handling
item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded:
• Cold storage systems (coldstore.jpg)

We design cold storage systems to extend the shelf life of perishable agricultural commodities. We also provide temporary storage of your harvest to wait for a good market price in case you need one.

  • Market linkages

We know that farmers spend most of their time taking care of their crops in the field expecting for higher yields and eventually profit. We use our network of buyers to connect you to the market so you can sell your products at a reasonable price.

  • Transportation

We have specialized trucks for moving your produces to the market without affecting the quality. Our logistics department can be reached at any time.

  • Packaging and value addition

Sometimes you produce the product, but you have an idea to turn it into something else, we are also glad to provide a number of ideas for adding value to your products and hence increasing quality and profit.

item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded:

Greenhouse Installation

Crop growth depends on several factors such as nutrients, humidity, sunlight, water etc. It is not always possible to manage these conditions in an open field. . At Kasong Agrotech we integrate modern technology in agriculture and IoT to monitor the crop growth factors so that our farmers can get better yields. We build greenhouses to protect you from variation of outside environment so you can produce crops year-round.

Our greenhouses can be customized to meet your demands. We install greenhouses from fully automated to manually operated. With our greenhouses you will ensure high productivity and year-round yield.

See Our Greenhouse Varieties below

Start Farming With us now

item.title: Services
item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded:
OUR Services

It\'s Time to start farming with us

We offer a wide range of services which will ensure that your farm is healthy and productive. Our services high standard services are provided by our experts at affordable rates.

Farm Energy & Water Supply

If your farm is far from power supply line or you have no water source close by, you don\'t have to worry. We install a compliment power system including drilling wells or setting up a rain water harvesting system, this will make your farm to produce crops year round.

Greenhouse Installation

Our greenhouses can be customized to meet based on your demands. We install greenhouses from fully automated to manually operated. With our greenhouses you will ensure high productivity and year-round yield.

Drips & Sprinklers Irrigation

High water usage is among the factors lowering the farmers profit. conventional irrigation methods uses more water hence increasing your operating expenses. With our new technology you will be able to irrigate your field with the correct amount of water.

Farm Mechanization

The agriculture season starts with field preparation. we know know that small holder farmers don\'t have the capital to buy the heavy machinery. As Kasong AgroTech, we outsource our powerful agricultural machines to work on your farm.

Aquaculture & Fisheries

We are also experts in setting up and managing fish ponds. We design your fish pond from the scratch and we supply you with everything you need to get started including linking you to our experts network.

Seeds & Seedlings

Choosing the best seed variety assures you to have higher yields. With our experts we provide advice on the best type of the seeds to be used based on your soil composition and probable pests. Our seed varieties are resistant to pests and diseases.

Farm Design & Planning

It is always hard to know where to locate what in your piece of land. At Kasong AgroTech, we design your farm from the scratch to integrate animals and possibility for reuse of wastes from one system to the other with easy so you can produce everything from the same peace of land.

Market for Your Products

We know that farmers spend most of their time taking care of their crops expecting for higher yields and eventually profit. We use our network of buyers to connect you to the market so you can sell your products at a reasonable price.

Post Harvest Handling

We design cold storage systems to extend the shelf life of perishable agricultural commodities. We also provide temporary storage of your harvest to wait for a good market price in case you need one.

Our Clients

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: nick
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Suggested text: Our website address is: http:.

Comments

Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

Suggested text: If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Cookies

Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Who we share your data with

Suggested text: If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.

How long we retain your data

Suggested text: If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

Suggested text: If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where your data is sent

Suggested text: Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.
